text: Waiting time for takeaway way too long don't come. Waited for 1hr

Dinner in Chaozhou City is truly unforgettable. The ingredients are fresh, the cooking is exquisite, you will have endless aftertaste after eating, and the service is very good. I recommend it to everyone who loves food.

It's a restaurant with a great environment. It's very comfortable to sit down, dine, and chat. It's a full sense of ceremony. Every dish is delicious and exquisite, and the service is also very attentive!
